Bioshock Fixes for Steam Deck
Fixes to launch Bioshock game on Steam after introduction of new 2k launcher
Bioshock Remastered

    Enter the line below into launch option in games properties

bash -c 'exec "${@/2KLauncher/LauncherPatcher.exe/Build/Final/BioshockHD.exe}"'
Bioshock 2 Remastered

    Enter the line below into launch option in games properties

bash -c 'exec "${@/2KLauncher/LauncherPatcher.exe/Build/Final/BioshockHD2.exe}"'
Bioshock Infinite
Change to compatible mode with Proton 7.0+

    Enter the line below into launch option in games properties

bash -c 'exec "${@/2KLauncher/LauncherPatcher.exe/Binaries/Win32/BioShockInfinite.exe}"' -- %command% -nointro 
